dc_title_s: Sea Lamprey Larval Max Extent, Great Lakes Region 2017
dc_description_s: A layer indicating the farthest historic upstream observation of sea lamprey larvae based on surveys conducted by the Larval Assessment Task Force. Lines were generated using survey point data as input for geometric network analysis along the NHD hydro network.
